title: New Zealand DEM Hillshade
description: Hillshade generated from the New Zealand LiDAR 1m DEM and New Zealand Contour-Derived 8m DEM (where no 1m DEM data exists) using GDAL’s default hillshading parameters of 315˚ azimuth and 45˚ elevation angle.
